OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEastern
OL,6,Fparts of Wales may catch a shower
OL,7,Fearly this evening, but much of the
OL,8,Fcountry will be dry with sunny, then
OL,9,Fclear spells. Overnight, low cloud
OL,10,Fwill edge in from the east, bringing
OL,11,Fpatchy drizzle and hill fog.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FA bright start in the west,
OL,14,Fbut on the whole Tuesday will be a
OL,15,Fcloudy day, with patchy drizzle and
OL,16,Fsome hill fog initially. Skies
OL,17,Fbrightening up towards the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
