OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FMostly
OL,6,Ffine on Wednesday and Thursday with
OL,7,Fsome warm sunshine, though feeling
OL,8,Fcooler in the brisk easterly wind.
OL,9,FCloudier with showers on Friday,
OL,10,Fthough more humid, with lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
